---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const updated = '2026-06-19'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer — oriz"
  description="What oriz is and isn't."
  wordmarkSubtitle="legal"
>
  <header class="spine page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">oriz</a> / <a href="/legal/">legal</a> / disclaimer</p>
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </header>

  <article class="spine prose">
    <p>
      Everything on oriz.in is published in good faith for general information only. Use it at
      your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>Not financial advice</h2>
    <p>
      The finance and cards sections show calculators and reference data. They are not investment,
      tax, or insurance advice. Returns shown are computed from inputs you provide; they are not
      predictions. Consult a SEBI-registered investment advisor before making financial
      decisions.
    </p>
    <p>
      oriz, its operator, and its contributors do not recommend, endorse, or assume responsibility
      for any product, service, or institution discussed on these sites.
    </p>

    <h2>Not medical advice</h2>
    <p>
      Anything related to health is for general awareness. It is not a substitute for consultation
      with a registered medical practitioner.
    </p>

    <h2>Not legal advice</h2>
    <p>
      Articles touching on tax, regulation, or compliance reflect the author's reading of the
      rules at the time of writing. Rules change. Verify with your own counsel before acting.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      We link to third-party sites we find useful. We don't control their content, and inclusion
      is not an endorsement.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Where applicable, oriz may earn a referral fee when you sign up to a service via certain
      links. This never affects what we recommend, and any such links will be marked.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
